<dl id="n05029e"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n05" href="#n05029e">N05 (VI.B.2)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n05all.htm#n05029e"> 29(e)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> annual hero = God</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">The transition from Anthropophagy to theophagy was extremely subtle. In some instances a captive was taken at random; in others, a young man, of unblemished body, was selected to <mark>represent the Supreme Being for a year</mark>. <small> J.T. Lloyd, <a name="GODE" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#GODE"><cite title="source">God-Eating</cite></a>, (1921) 40</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
